{"id":"c7b98c74-2a0e-4560-8797-6310553db193","type":"main-list-block","metadata":{"filename":"1512-10-[c7b98c74].json","folder":"michelangelo-letters","focus":{"blockId":"deb508ec-bc51-4da6-b48b-6850f8839ab7","caret":107}},"blockProperties":[],"children":[{"id":"17879425-c69e-46bb-85f1-4319bcfd84e2","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, [October, 1512].\r","standoffProperties":[{"id":"2589a870-067d-4f1e-932b-a8131fde2da6","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","text":"Rom","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"4b29b87b-a581-409b-ba31-575b2058135a","type":"codex/time-reference","start":12,"end":24,"value":"a50aee6a-2e37-47f7-b3db-464eb6ff2e03","text":"October, 151","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false}],"blockProperties":[{"id":"90c1e114-7cce-4881-9d73-863980c234aa","type":"block/alignment/right","metadata":{},"isDeleted":false}],"children":[],"metadata":{},"relation":{}},{"id":"b4cd27bb-ab5b-4b85-95a0-22ac6b754d15","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lodovico di Buonarrota Simoni,\r","standoffProperties":[{"id":"2ea73772-553b-4d93-9899-fc41a3772082","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":31,"value":"","text":"To Lodovico di Buonarrota Simon","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"236713b0-f0aa-487f-adc0-398128f0c1fd","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"21671569-3eea-412b-85cc-08f659f58019","text":"Lodovico di Buonarrota Simon","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false}],"blockProperties":[{"id":"7d2b1657-e057-4fb6-94cb-b2ed3f84c2a8","type":"block/alignment/right","metadata":{},"isDeleted":false}],"children":[],"metadata":{},"relation":{}},{"id":"442d7ae1-6c8a-41fa-ac06-fe5b6a060553","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.\r","standoffProperties":[{"id":"3bde09c6-990c-4ae4-a476-ab5b0172e7de","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","text":"Florenc","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false}],"blockProperties":[{"id":"15b43634-b48b-4642-924e-919a0531ebcf","type":"block/alignment/right","metadata":{},"isDeleted":false}],"children":[],"metadata":{},"relation":{}},{"id":"44cce770-3e68-44e8-8402-d323374689d6","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"\r","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[],"children":[],"metadata":{},"relation":{}},{"id":"7ddf7776-922b-4299-842e-1df7de6e55ea","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Dearest Father, — In your last letter you tell me to be careful not to keep money in the house and not to carry any about with me; also that I am reported in Florence as having spoken against the Medici.\r","standoffProperties":[{"id":"d29404af-6451-43ce-953d-26125e31f8c6","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":13,"value":"","text":"Dearest Fathe","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"bdb35079-bd08-4d20-8354-8f6229e3b9df","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":13,"value":"21671569-3eea-412b-85cc-08f659f58019","text":"Dearest Fathe","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"681cae1c-8d1f-4df4-9a16-2ce8123cb647","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":21,"end":24,"value":"21671569-3eea-412b-85cc-08f659f58019","text":"you","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"80428731-8abf-4e66-bf5d-6d2255fed659","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":38,"end":40,"value":"21671569-3eea-412b-85cc-08f659f58019","text":"yo","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"fc1577fd-8b65-45a8-820b-d39ef1ede827","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":47,"end":48,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","text":"m","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"4170c895-a71c-450e-9165-e3621b137939","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":127,"end":128,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","text":"m","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"27a1fd08-9177-4c7c-88ef-462f4a89fec5","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":141,"end":141,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","text":"","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"9d14cd50-620b-4613-9e25-fdaf8c045a1b","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":158,"end":165,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","text":"Florenc","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"47a66fd2-3b82-4687-b6e0-d695fbb9fda6","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":196,"end":201,"value":"f58ed5e3-a380-4e53-aa74-f7a8e7e7b3eb","text":"Medic","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false}],"blockProperties":[],"children":[],"metadata":{},"relation":{}},{"id":"bc562b59-20b1-40a6-a79b-7f45f75242cf","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"\r","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[],"children":[],"metadata":{},"relation":{}},{"id":"deb508ec-bc51-4da6-b48b-6850f8839ab7","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"As to the money, all I have lies in Balducci's bank, and I keep none of it either in the house nor upon my person, except such sums as are necessary from day to day. With regard to the Medici, I have never uttered a single word against them except in the general terms in which everybody talks — as, for instance, about the Prato affair. I think that even the very stones would have spoken of it, had they been able. There have been many other things said since then, to which, when I heard them, I have always replied :— \"If they are really doing these things, they are doing wrong.\" Not that I believed the reports, and God grant they be not true. About a month ago someone who pretended to be my friend criticised their actions very adversely. I rebuked him, saying that those who spoke in such a way did wrong, and that he was not to mention the subject to me again. However, I should like Buonarroto to find out quietly where the man in question heard that I had spoken against the Medici, so that I may endeavour to trace the origin of the rumour, and find out whether it came from someone professing to be my friend. I shall then be upon my guard. I have nothing more to add. As yet I have begun nothing, and I am waiting until the Pope tells me what I am to do.\r","standoffProperties":[{"id":"78dbeb71-ddc4-44c0-bdc1-0dca25a75387","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":21,"end":21,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","text":"","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"6f004f00-5ecc-4365-9d19-b4bc7ffebf42","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":36,"end":43,"value":"24535c01-687a-4e00-bb3f-b9b0f446e6ab","text":"Balducc","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"ebe573e9-fe0b-4bdd-8778-5f59ab6a2072","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":57,"end":57,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","text":"","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"da5a701c-9725-4d0c-8d32-51393c5624aa","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":104,"end":105,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","text":"m","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"a89110e1-c0ad-4813-aea4-3f603bd8c061","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":185,"end":190,"value":"f58ed5e3-a380-4e53-aa74-f7a8e7e7b3eb","text":"Medic","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"57b34a81-a5cd-4091-8b37-12f36850695c","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":193,"end":193,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","text":"","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"b33ef341-fe66-462b-8674-56e792bbdd77","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":324,"end":328,"value":"ed1f1c87-b209-44cb-9818-6a86b8f89dc6","text":"Prat","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"78e7dfff-7d17-4193-a350-a120be0a1c30","type":"codex/document-reference","start":336,"end":336,"value":"5d186b0e-138e-47b8-8096-2c097ef6f828","text":"","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"e93f52f0-6202-4e7d-8e06-a832639b5cfd","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":338,"end":338,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","text":"","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"cc30eb0e-5334-